00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:13,840
[Episode 11]

3
00:01:14,690 --> 00:01:16,920
The so-called "Melodic Recognition"

4
00:01:17,150 --> 00:01:18,930
involves five Guqin players performing

5
00:01:18,930 --> 00:01:21,660
five different pieces of music simultaneously.

6
00:01:21,710 --> 00:01:22,420
The first party

7
00:01:22,420 --> 00:01:23,700
to distinguish all five pieces

8
00:01:23,700 --> 00:01:25,230
amidst the cacophony wins.

9
00:02:16,510 --> 00:02:17,420
Grieving Spirit,

10
00:02:17,420 --> 00:02:18,910
Palace Secret Rhythm,

11
00:02:18,930 --> 00:02:20,170
West Wind's Fury,

12
00:02:38,910 --> 00:02:39,780
Mysterious Orchid,

13
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:41,120
and Mulberry Tree of the Path.

14
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,560
Feng Qiwu gave up.

15
00:02:42,590 --> 00:02:44,850
Sangyi's man guessed the five pieces first.

16
00:02:44,850 --> 00:02:45,980
We're going to lose.

17
00:02:47,370 --> 00:02:48,770
It's all my fault

18
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,710
that the academy...

19
00:02:52,829 --> 00:02:54,660
